name: eslint-plugin-compat

scripts.build: cross-env NODE_ENV=production rm -rf lib && babel src --out-dir lib
scripts.test: yarn lint && yarn build && cross-env NODE_ENV=test yarn spec
scripts.test-all: cross-env NODE_ENV=test yarn lint && yarn flow && yarn spec && yarn build
